  "title": "Support Staff (Technical / Programme)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will perform quality checks on online learning programmes, collaborate with technical teams to troubleshoot LMS content issues, provide Level 1 technical support to stakeholders, and assist with programme management and logistical tasks to support the ILT team.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform quality checks on online learning programmes to ensure content accuracy and proper functionality on the LMS</li><li>Collaborate with technical teams to identify and resolve technical issues related to content building and delivery on the LMS</li><li>Provide Level 1 technical support to stakeholders by troubleshooting content and platform issues promptly</li><li>Communicate clearly with clients to understand their needs and deliver timely, effective solutions</li><li>Support Instructor-Led Training (ILT) activities by coordinating programmes and managing logistical tasks</li><li>Adapt quickly to new systems, processes, and tools to enhance support capabilities</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Basic knowledge of Learning Management Systems (LMS) or e-learning platforms.</li><li>Ability to perform quality checks on online learning programmes to ensure content accuracy and functionality.</li><li>Willingness to provide Level 1 technical support and assist with basic troubleshooting of content and platform issues.</li><li>Comfortable collaborating with technical teams to resolve issues.</li><li>Good communication skills to support stakeholders and understand their needs.</li><li>Strong attention to detail and basic organizational skills.</li><li>Willingness to support ILT activities, including programme coordination and logistical tasks.</li><li>Open to learning new systems, processes, and tools.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Salary: $2650/month</li><li>Working Arrangement: Mon-Fri</li><li>Working Location: Buona Vista</li><li>Contract Period: 6 months</li></ul><p><br />EA License No: 96C4864<br />Reg. No.: R24121728 EUNICE WOO JING QI</p>",
